#: ../../source/userguides/buildings_model.rst:11
#: 3364ab3140b949e8b6f52a4033bc47d0
msgid ""
"The model does not extract the footprints directly, because they are not "
"clearly visible in the images, but it can obtain them, just like human "
"cartographers, by moving the roof to the bottom of the wall (see "
"Additional options)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/userguides/buildings_model.rst:13
